22:39.230 --> 22:40.600
seseorang akan mendapat

22:41.040 --> 22:42.190
dan mengubah masa lalu dan masa depan.

22:43.950 --> 22:45.560
Hari kemusnahan?

22:46.710 --> 22:48.360
Pakcik Zhaoyou, berhenti!

22:49.080 --> 22:49.750
Ayah!

22:53.710 --> 22:54.430
Ayah!

22:55.470 --> 22:56.160
[Susu,]

22:56.880 --> 22:57.990
[bila kita ada peluang]

